<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb52be26e-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d" identifier="/us/usc/t6/s491"><num value="491">§ 491.</num><heading> National Homeland Security Council</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is established within the Executive Office of the President a council to be known as the “Homeland Security Council” (in this subchapter referred to as the “Council”).</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb52be26f-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d">(<ref href="/us/pl/107/296/tIX/s901">Pub. L. 107–296, title IX, § 901</ref>, <date date="2002-11-25">Nov. 25, 2002</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/116/2258">116 Stat. 2258</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
